eu.socialsensor.graphbased.clust

Class Community<V,E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.socialsensor.graphbased.clust.Community<V,E>

  • public class Community<V,E>
extends Object
    Data class that models a node community. The community is identified by an id field and is always defined with reference to a Graph object (which shouldn't be modified) To specify the members of the community, a list of objects is necessary. Obviously, the objects need to be contained in the graph.
    Author:
    papadop
